{"tid":2322394,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"秀智慶祝出道十週年　月底開線上演唱會！","createTime":"2020-12-12T09:48:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-12T11:34:21.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"413526135461df245aafdfd7bc755c39c102a822","tid":2322394,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T09:48:50.000Z","msg":"隨著《Start-Up》完結，近年來都以影劇活動為主的秀智即將久違地重拾歌手身分，在月底舉行特別的線上演唱會！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nManagement SOOP 本週宣布秀智將於 12 月 23 日晚間 7 點（韓國時間），經由 Kakao TV、1theK、1theK Original 頻道直播個人線上演唱會《Suzy: A Tempo》。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_abc13aec922f2158a50baee053cb5a09/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-12/132274-888631.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_abc13aec922f2158a50baee053cb5a09%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-12%2F132274-888631.jpg&h=d2eed42f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&ldquo;A Tempo&rdquo; 為代表「速度還原」的音樂術語，用在樂曲暫時改變速度後回歸全曲原速的時刻。秀智便以這個術語作為演唱會名稱，意味著將透過《Suzy: A Tempo》回顧一路忙碌地度過的十年並調整步調，無論往後遇到什麼樣的變化，都不會為之動搖。<br />\n<br />\n特別的是，秀智從 9 月便開始親自參與《Suzy: A Tempo》的企劃工作，用心準備這場久違的粉絲活動。在演唱會登場前，就先聽聽她最近為《Start-Up》唱的 OST 吧！"},{"pid":"db3d1159375ef3aa16dc9409d86c83f21a5f9863","tid":2322394,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T10:01:57.000Z","msg":"建築學概論<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edf1edd298873d1cc39d3b65076ab6610b70585a","tid":2322394,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T11:12:55.000Z","msg":"支持！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64f263628c5a9bb9bd924e2d18ff64a07214d5e0","tid":2322394,"uid":294121,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T11:28:27.000Z","msg":"過哂氣<br />\n我睇aespa唔好"},{"pid":"cd023ed80a8cf8c69780fa43e054fd5e23019cce","tid":2322394,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T11:34:21.000Z","msg":"秀智睽違6年在台灣開騷，可惜票房未如理想，台灣傳媒指主辦單位聲稱全場2000個座位售出八成，但實際現場僅安排了不足900個座位，當中入座約七成，即僅有600名粉絲到場，料票房達200萬台幣（約52萬港元）。"}]}